34→// Restrict browser-root auto-attach to extension-relevant target types.
35→// Excluding page/iframe prevents third-party OAuth popups (claude.ai, Google, etc.)
36→// from being pulled into our CDP session, which Chrome flags as "a debugger is
37→// attached" and surfaces as "Debugger paused in another tab" when those popups
38→// ship anti-debug `debugger;` statements. enableAutoAttach() below stays filter-less
39→// for the unified-logging path, which needs page coverage.
